	Update url with 404 status on LEGAL file.

	  * Update redirected and upstream url.
	  * Added the Wayback Machine url for missing link.

	  [Bug #12762][ruby-dev:49802]

	From: SHIBATA Hiroshi <hsbt@ruby-lang.org>
